<h4 id="id-(3.15)MREArchitecture&amp;CommunicationFlow-MediaRoutingFeatures&amp;Definitions" style=""><span id="MREArchitecture&amp;amp;CommunicationFlow-MediaRoutingFeatures&amp;amp;Definitions"></span><strong>Media Routing Features &amp; Definitions </strong>
