         <tr>
          <th>
           <p>Scenario</p>
          </th>
          <th colspan="1">
           <p>State</p>
          </th>
          <th>
           <p>Description</p>
          </th>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
           <p>If the agent is in between a conversation but the state is pending not ready</p>
          </td>
          <td colspan="1">
           <p>PENDING_NOT_READY</p>
          </td>
          <td>
           <p>No more tasks will be routed to the agent until he changes his state from pending not ready to the ready state.</p>
          </td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
