   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h3>
<p>As per current release, here are limitations regarding MRE, Mre-Microservice &amp; MRE-UI:</p>
<ul>
 <li>
  <p>Attributes must not be deleted in MRE-UI, otherwise unexpected behavior cannot be avoided</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Precision queues can be updated but not be deleted in MRE-UI, if a precision queue is deleted, MRE will need to be restarted to take effect</p>
 </li>
</ul>
